00:43.467 --> 00:46.112
I'll turn to God when I get old, and then he will receive my soul.

00:47.033 --> 00:51.261
One Friday morning she was taken ill.

00:51.822 --> 00:56.910
Her stubborn heart began to yield.

00:58.213 --> 01:02.440
Alas, alas, my days are spent.

01:02.961 --> 01:07.669
Too late to go now to repent.

01:08.105 --> 01:33.977
