01:34.227 --> 02:00.910
My soul is lost and doomed to hell. Those hellish flames they round me roll. Oh, I'm a lost and ruined soul. She gnawed her tongue before she died. She wrung her hands and screamed and cried.

02:01.126 --> 02:22.830
Oh, must I burn forevermore Ten thousand years all o'er and o'er. Young people now, both great and small Take warning by my dying words

02:27.097 --> 02:31.217
